An explosion at the Ghadir steel
plant in central  Iran  killed seven people and injured 12 others,
the state-run Mehr news agency reported, citing Azizollah Seifi,
the provinceâ€™s governor.  The incident occurred at 9:15 p.m. local time yesterday
